  m_Name: DialogNPCTutorial
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  Name: Rocco (Roger 11Labs)
  Icon: {fileID: -2105629146, guid: d556a7f542c7d03429c5a535ce31a084, type: 3}
  HasInteraction: 0
  interactionType: 3
  Greeting: Hey...
  Day1Dialog:
  - "Hey\u2026 now that you\u2019re awake, be careful wandering around. This place
    isn\u2019t safe anymore.\n\nPRESS F FOR MORE \u2192"
  - "If you\u2019re looking for something to do, seek out the French knight Pierre
    de Massues-Vercoiran, known as Colonel Mas. He\u2019s asking for extra hands.\n\nThere
    are other soldiers around the fort who might have some insight of what is happening. 
    Try to talk to everyone you can!"
  Day2FirstTimeDialog:
  - "You\u2019re still here. Most people try to disappear after the first night.\n\nYou
    must have something in you to stay with us. Jean Parisot de Valette doesn\u2019t
    want us to abandon this fort. He wants us to hold it until the end.\n\nPRESS
    F FOR MORE \u2192"
  - "I might never see my family again. Try to help around the fort \u2014 it matters
    more than you think.\n\nIf you\u2019re looking for something to do, head down
    to the infirmary. They need help with the wounded soldiers.\n\nSome of them might
    live another day\u2026 and return to their families."
  Day2MetBeforeDialog:
  - "You\u2019re still here. Most people try to disappear after the first night. 
    You must have something in you to keep you here with us.  Jean Pierre De La Vallette
    does not want us to leave this fort.  He wants us to hold it till the end. \n\nPRESS
    F FOR MORE -->"
  - "I might not see my family again.  Try to help around the fort.  That matters
    more than you think.\nIf you\u2019re looking for something to do, why don't you
    head down to the infirmary.  They could use your help with the wounded soldiers. 
    They get to live another day, go back to their families!"
  Day3FirstTimeDialog:
  - "I had a family outside these walls once.\n\nI hope they\u2019re safe in Birgu.
    I know I won\u2019t be \u2014 not here.\n\nIf you\u2019re still searching for
    someone, don\u2019t stop. Hope is the only thing that lasts longer than these
    stones."
  Day3MetBeforeDialog:
  - "I had a family outside these walls once.\n\nI hope they\u2019re safe in Birgu.
    I know I won\u2019t be \u2014 not here.\n\nIf you\u2019re still searching for
    someone, don\u2019t stop. Hope is the only thing that lasts longer than these
    stones."
  Day4FirstTimeDialog:
  - "Be careful, boy. Turgut Reis \u2014 we call him Dragut \u2014 has joined the
    fight.\n\nThe bombardment has intensified. He\u2019s not just a corsair \u2014
    he\u2019s a military genius.\n\nHe\u2019s set cannons on both sides of the fort
    now."
  Day4MetBeforeDialog:
  - "Be careful, boy. Turgut Reis \u2014 we call him Dragut \u2014 has joined the
    fight.\n\nThe bombardment has intensified. He\u2019s not just a corsair \u2014
    he\u2019s a military genius.\n\nHe\u2019s set cannons on both sides of the fort
    now."
  Day5FirstTimeDialog:
  - "Whatever happens today\u2026 you did what you could.\n\nThat counts \u2014 even
    if no one remembers our names.\n\nOnly nobles are written down. Not us. The common
    people.\n\nPRESS F FOR MORE \u2192"
  - "We fight, we bleed, we die\u2026 and no one remembers.\n\nNo one will remember
    me."
  Day5MetBeforeDialog:
  - "Whatever happens today\u2026 you did what you could.\n\nThat counts \u2014 even
    if no one remembers our names.\n\nOnly nobles are written down. Not us. The common
    people.\n\nPRESS F FOR MORE \u2192"
  - "We fight, we bleed, we die\u2026 and no one remembers.\n\nNo one will remember
    me."
